# Services Layer
#
# Contains business logic, one file per domain:
#   authService.js         — credential validation, OTP management
#   adminService.js        — statistics, approvals
#   doctorService.js       — slot management, clinic profiles
#   vendorService.js       — inventory management
#   appointmentService.js  — booking with pessimistic locking, escrow payout
#   orderService.js        — order placement with split-payment logic
#   chatService.js         — message persistence
#   emailService.js        — nodemailer SMTP email delivery
#   otpService.js          — OTP generation, TTL-based storage, verification
#
# Rule: Services must:
#   - Orchestrate one or more repository calls
#   - Enforce all business rules (e.g., "slot must be available", "fee >= 0")
#   - Throw ApiError for rule violations
#   - Never touch req or res objects
#
# Populated in: Milestone 6 (Services)
